@startuml
title Donation Processing Workflow -D2C- 

start
:Admin triggers WhatsApp scan;
:Extract wallet addresses\nand campaign links;
if (Campaign exists?) then (no)
  :Create new campaign\nwith extracted data;
else (yes)
  :Update existing campaign;
endif

:Admin imports Whydonate payout;
:Calculate 4-line totals\nand convert to EUR;
:Use Stripe exchange rates\nfor conversion;

:Donations accumulate in EUR;
:Admin initiates batch conversion;

:Batch sent to Simplex\nvia Atomic Wallet;
:Convert EUR to USDT;
:Send USDT via Tron network;
:Confirm transaction\non blockchain;

stop

@enduml